channel.title: Comments on: Tyrone McCloskey’s JFK art installation up now at Kezar Bar and Restaurant

item.title: By: Tyrone Mccloskey
item.dc:creator: Tyrone Mccloskey
item.description:
Very likely this Friday at 6pm, CBS local affiliate KPIX will air a short piece on the show which was shot last night featuring me holding forth about JFK, art therapy and whatnot- Very little conspiracy crazy was offered by Yours C. Truly* so everyone exhale-
*No relation to Roy S. Truly, superintendent of the Texas School Book Depository-
